high_descs: Turn left, turn left, walk straight, turn right to the table next to the sink
Pick up the knife on the table
Cut the bread on the table into slices
Turn right, walk straight, turn left to the microwave
Open the microwave, put the knife inside, close the microwave.
Turn left, walk straight, turn right to the table next to the sink
Pick up a slice of bread from the table
Turn right, walk straight, turn left to the fridge
Open the fridge, put the bread inside, close the fridge. Open the fridge, take out the bread inside, close the fridge.
Turn left, walk straight, turn right to microwave
Open the microwave, put the bread inside, close the microwave.

high_descs: Turn left and step forward to face the counter.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Cut the bread on the counter into slices.
Step right to face the microwave.
Place the knife in the microwave.
Step to the left to face the bread on the counter.
Pick up a slice of bread on the counter.
Turn right and walk forward and turn left to face the fridge.
Cool the bread slice in the fridge and remove it.
Step to the left to face the microwave.
Place the bread slice in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: To cool a bread slice and place it in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn around, go forward, turn right before the sink
Pick up the knife on the counter
Slice the bread on the counter
Move a bit to the right to the front of the microwave
Put the knife in the microwave
Move a bit to the left
Pick up a bread slice from the counter
Turn right,go forward, turn left at the fridge
Put the bread slice in the fridge, wait, pick up the bread slice from the fridge
Turn left, go forward, turn right at the microwave
Put the bread in the microwave
